WEBVTT

13:40.431 --> 13:43.561
<b>Wouldn't it be a good opportunity
for him to enjoy</b>

13:43.631 --> 13:45.501
<b>a leisurely overseas trip?</b>

13:45.971 --> 13:48.631
<b>That's right. They'll be coming
at our expense, after all.</b>

13:49.541 --> 13:54.071
<b>Thank you very much.
I am completely indebted to you, sir.</b>
